### TESTS API CEPIC
### Utiliser avec REST Client (VS Code extension) ou Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### 1. TEST SANTÉ DU SERVEUR
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 2. LISTE DES FORMATIONS (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/trainings

### 3. CATÉGORIES
GET {{baseUrl}}/trainings/categories

### 4. DÉTAIL FORMATION (remplacer {id} par un vrai ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/trainings/clzxxx

### 5. LOGIN ADMIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@cepic.ci",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 6. LOGIN USER
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 7. CRÉER INSCRIPTION (nécessite auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "trainingId": "TRAINING_ID_HERE"
}

### 8. MES INSCRIPTIONS (nécessite auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Cookie: auth_token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. GALERIE PHOTOS
GET {{baseUrl}}/gallery

### 10. ENVOYER MESSAGE CONTACT
POST {{baseUrl}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "0123456789",
  "subject": "Test",
  "message": "Message de test"
}
